    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and project seekers! This vehicle is ready for a second lease on life and offers a fantastic starting point for someone handy with a wrench. While it currently needs significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it\u2019s a budget-friendly way to get your hands on this model. Grab this project car today and make it your own!",
